'5:10': [
{sup:1, word:"with", lines:["This indicates that David had God&rsquo;s presence. Moreover, Hiram&rsquo;s helping David to build himself a house and David&rsquo;s victory over the Philistines (vv. {2Sa5:11|11}-{2Sa5:25|25}) were outward confirmations from God in David&rsquo;s environment. If we are one with God for the accomplishing of His economy, we will always have the inward presence of God and the outward confirmation in our environment."]},
],
